_source.text: A cast that is better known in America might have filled more seats in the Dorothy Chandler Pavilion, but it is hard to believe that they would be superior, or even as good, as the youthful ensemble currently singing (and acting and cavorting) energetically in this production of "Così Fan Tutte."

_source.text: 06/23/10 Bristol, Tn. - Mustang engineer Seong Park is congratulated by Tim Duerr of Ford Racing after the 2011 Mustang V6 finally coasted to a stop on the backstretch of Bristol Motor Speedway after completeing 1,457 laps and averaging better than 48 MPG over the distance of the Mustang 1000 Lap Challenge.
